snippet.title: Paper Beast Enhanced Edition - Release Date Trailer | PS5 & PS VR2 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/paper-beast/

Paper Beast Enhanced Edition will be launched for the PS VR2 and PS5 on September 27th, 2023. The original game was praised for its innovative gameplay, unique aesthetics, and extraordinary universe. This mesmerizing adventure fully leverages the capabilities of the PSVR2 and PS5, offering enhanced features and improved immersion.

Paper Beast © 2016-2023 Pixel Reef
